properties.code: The ISO 3-character currency code. For example, `USD`.
properties.symbol: The symbol of the currency. For example, `$`.
properties.symbol_native: The native symbol of the currency, if it has a different local symbol.
properties.name: The name of the currency
properties.decimal_digits: How many digits are after the decimal separator for prices in this currency.
properties.rounding: The rounding percision of prices in this currency.
